reviewText: The first part was various pow wow dances, and then it went into healing flute tunes, and the last part is Chief Silverheels giving a sermon.  Overal it is a good program.

They were poorly filmed exerpts of Pow Wows. If you want to go to a Pow Wow, and I have been to many and love them, get in the car and go to one. I expected something totally different in this DVD, especially being when you named it "Gospel". I was very dissapointed.
